title: Xbox Series X Launch Day Has Arrived! - Kinda Funny Games Daily 11.10.20
description:
00:00:00 - Start
00:04:10 - Housekeeping
Our First Impressions video of The Pathless is now live on youtube.com/KindaFunnyGames and on podcast services
This Friday, Andy’s streaming some of the Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War campaign with his fancy PC to show off Ray Tracing and his Nvidia RTX 3080 (Sponsored By Nvidia). That’s happening 2-4PM pacific time, Friday on twitch.tv/kindafunnygames
Thank you to our Patreon Producers:Tom Bock & Black Jack
The Roper Report   -
00:07:50 - It’s Xbox Launch Day!
00:18:10 - Some Amazon Xbox Series X pre-orders may not arrive until December - Marie Dealessandri @ GiBiz
00:22:20 - How does Walmart screw this up so bad? - Best Friends Q:Startroop1
00:25:30+ - The Pathless Review round up
00:32:37 - PSVR game Blood and Truth is enhanced for PS5
00:41:10 - Ori and The Will of The Wisp’s next-gen upgrade has been detailed
00:44:30 -  Ad  
00:49:10 - You’ll be able to transfer your Spider-Man PS4 save
00:52:45 - Take Two buying Codemasters has been finalized and is official - Joseph Knoop @ IGN
00:55:00 - Out today
01:02:00 - You‘re Wrong
Tomorrow’s Hosts:Greg and Gary Whitta
